OL,5, Doctors are prescribing heating to     
OL,6, patients with conditions that get worse
OL,7, in the cold as part of a health trial. 
OL,9,FThe Warm Home Prescription pilot paid  
OL,10,Fto heat the homes of 28 low-income     
OL,11,Fpatients to avoid the cost of hospital 
OL,12,Fcare if they became more ill.          
OL,14,FThe trial achieved such good results it
OL,15,Fis being expanded to 1,150 homes.      
OL,17,FMichelle Davis, who has arthritis and  
OL,18,Fserious pulmonary illness, had her     
OL,19,Fenergy bills paid for and said the     
OL,20,Fdifference was "mind-blowing".         
